The paper deals with generating responses in visual dialog, which involves natural language processing and computer vision, making it likely to belong to the categories of cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel training paradigm inspired by reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves training a neural network, which is a common theme in the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
